@node _get_dev_info, io
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <io.h>

short _get_dev_info(int arg);
@end example

@subheading Description

Given drive_number (A: = 0, B: = 1, etc.) or a file handle in @var{arg},
this function returns the device info word which is returned by DOS IOCTL
function 0 (Int 21h/AX=4400h).  In case of error, -1 is returned and
@var{errno} is set.


@subheading Portability

@portability !ansi, !posix

